  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors are fully assessed; achievedLevel meets or exceeds requiredLevel for every factor. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed and documented. Decision: Accepted — the model demonstrates sufficient credibility for the intended COU.",
