      },
      "rationale": "Geometric fidelity confirmed via CMM measurement of the FDA pump impeller (max deviation 0.05 mm from nominal CAD). Fluid properties matched to within experimental measurement uncertainty. Boundary condition equivalency table documented in the V&V report Appendix B. No input parameter deviations with material impact on NIH identified. Level 4 met."
